<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Ysemang<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir in <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> cze rede gesaczt. Nu spricht er, daz er
                        alspald darauf kein völlig <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> getün müg, wan er
                                <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd, der er darczu bedürff,
                                <expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nicht
                            <expan>gehab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> müg. Aber er main, daz er ew
                            <add>des</add> ynwendig dreyen <expan>woch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöll, und hat uns
                            <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir ew
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen, daz <add>ir</add> es die weil
                        also <expan>gütlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> besteen lasset. Und also
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir das
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> tün wöllet. Und wo etc.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> oculi.</ab>
